    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 9th level, select one taijutsu or bukijutsu you know. </p><p>The selected jutsu gains the Medical Keyword. </p><p>You may select an additional taijutsu or bukijutsu at 13th and 17th level to gain the Medical Keyword this way. </p><p>You may switch which jutsu this feature affects when you would complete a Long Rest. </p><p>Also, you can attack twice, instead of once, whenever you take the Attack action on your turn.</p>",
